

CONVERTERS
=============



NAME OF THE CONVERTER          FILENAME
---------------------------------------------------
1. CLP to WX                   clp2wx.pl
2. ISCII to Roman(WX)          ir
3. ISCII to UTF8               iscii2utf8.py
4. ISCII to Unicode            iscii-to-unicode.out
5. Itrans to ISCII             itrans-iscii.sh
6. Itrans to RA                itrans_ra.out
7.Harvard Kyoto to RA         kyoto_ra.out 
8.Logical to Itrans           logical_itrans.out
9.Roman to ISCII              ri_skt
10.Unicode to ISCII            unicode-iscii.out
11.Utf8 to ISCII               utf82iscii.pl
12.Utf8 to WX                  utf82wx.sh
13.Velthuis to WX              velthuis-wx.pl
14.WX to Utf8                  wx2utf8.sh
15.Makefile

Makefile 
---------------------
To run the make file type the following command
make

The following lex programs are compiled when the Makefile is run to produce the corresponding files with .out extension. 

ir.lex
iscii-to-unicode.lex
itrans_ra.lex
kyoto_ra.lex
logical_itrans.lex
ri.lex
ri_skt.lex
rm__between_vowels.lex
unicode-iscii.lex


HOW TO RUN THE CONVERTERS
===============================
inputfile is the input filename.
outputfile is the output filename. 




1. CLP to WX CONVERTER
-----------------------
perl clp2wx.pl < inputfile > ouputfile


2.ISCII to Roman CONVERTER
---------------------------
./ir < inputfile > outputfile

3.ISCII to UTF8 CONVERTER
--------------------------
./iscii2utf8.py script

    where script is a number between 1-9

    1 - devnag
    2 - bengali / assamese
    3 - punjabi
    4 - gujarati
    5 - oriya
    6 - tamil
    7 - telugu
    8 - kannada
    9 - malayalam

    the program reads from stdin and writes to stdout

    any msgs to the user (error msgs etc) are printed on stderr

./iscii2utf8.py 1 < inputfile > ouputfile


4.ISCII to Unicode CONVERTER
------------------------------
./iscii-to-unicode.out < inputfile > outputfile

5.Itrans to ISCII CONVERTER
------------------------------
sh itrans-iscii.sh < inputfile > ouptutfile

6.Itrans to RA CONVERTER
---------------------------
./itrans_ra.out < inputfile > ouputfile

7.Harvard Kyoto to RA converter
----------------------------------
./kyoto_ra.out < inputfile > outputfile

8.Logical to Itrans converter
--------------------------------
./logical_itrans.out < inputfile > ouputfile

9.Roman to ISCII converter
------------------------------
./ri_skt < inputfile > outputfile

10.Unicode to ISCII converter
---------------------------------
./unicode-iscii.out < inputfile > outputfile

11.utf8 to ISCII converter
------------------------------
perl utf82iscii.pl < inputfile > outputfile

12.utf8 to WX converter 
--------------------------
sh utf82wx.sh inputfile outputfile

13.Velthuis to WX converter
-----------------------------
perl velthuis-wx.pl < inputfile > outputfile

14.WX to utf8 converter
----------------------------
sh wx2utf8.sh inputfile ouputfile 



